HAPPY BIRTHDAY MATE
Master Product Bible (A–Z)

1. PRODUCT ESSENCE & VISION
Happy Birthday Mate is a global, ritual-based digital celebration platform built around one universal human truth: everyone has a birthday.
The platform exists to ensure that no one celebrates alone, to reveal the hidden joy of shared birthdays, and to transform birthdays from isolated personal events into collective global rituals.
Happy Birthday Mate is not a social network, not a messaging app, not a mental health platform, and not an event planner.
It is a time-bound celebration engine designed to:
•	Create anticipation
•	Enable joyful connection
•	Provide dignified recognition
•	Close celebrations gently
Wonder is created through timing, ritual, motion, and human presence, not through infinite content or algorithmic noise.

2. CORE PHILOSOPHY (NON NEGOTIABLE)
1.	Birthdays are the identity anchor
2.	Celebration is time bound and sacred
3.	Visibility is intentional and temporary
4.	Joy always precedes monetization
5.	Platform owned digital goods are primary
6.	Global first, Africa inclusive by design
7.	Emotional safety, privacy, and consent are foundational
8.	Ritual over engagement metrics
Every feature, rule, and exclusion exists to serve these principles.

3. TARGET AUDIENCE (FULLY INCLUSIVE)
•	All ages are welcome: from children to centenarians (0–100+)
•	Core digital engagement focus: ages 15–60
•	Elder inclusion (60+):
o	Family assisted onboarding allowed
o	Simplified UI modes
o	Celebration spotlight for elders
The platform celebrates life across generations.

4. USER ROLES
4.1 Registered User
•	Verified account
•	Automatically assigned to a birthday tribe
•	Can celebrate, host personal rooms, receive gifts
4.2 Invited Guest
•	Access via invite link
•	Can only participate in a specific personal birthday room
•	No tribe access
4.3 Admin / Moderator
•	Platform oversight
•	Moderation tools
•	Analytics access
•	No social participation
5. AUTHENTICATION & ONBOARDING
Authentication Methods
•	Email + password
•	Optional Google sign in
•	Service: Firebase Authentication
Required Signup Data
•	First name
•	Date of birth (MM DD used for tribe logic)
•	Gender (Male / Female / Prefer not to say)
•	Country
•	State
•	Profile picture (mandatory)
•	Consent confirmation (GDPR compliant)
Optional Data
•	City (text only, non precise)
Explicitly Excluded
•	Interests
•	Personality traits
•	Emotional diagnostics
•	Relationship data
•	Exact GPS location

6. USER PROFILE & IDENTITY
•	Profile picture is mandatory (users should be made to know why their photo is required).
•	Used across:
o	Homepage celebrant spiral
o	Birthday tribe rooms
o	Personal birthday rooms
o	State level celebrant visibility
Profile Change Rules
•	Can be changed up to 48 hours before birthday
•	Can be changed on birthday day
•	Rate limited and moderation protected

7. BIRTHDAY TRIBE SYSTEM (FOUNDATIONAL LOGIC)
Automatic Assignment
•	Users are automatically assigned to a tribe based on MM DD
•	Example: March 14 → Tribe 03 14
•	No browsing, joining, switching, or searching tribes
Tribe Lifecycle
•	Tribe is inactive outside the birthday
•	Unlocks ceremonially at 00:00 local time
•	Active for 24 hours
•	Auto closes and becomes read only
•	Closure is gentle and clearly communicated

8. BIRTHDAY TRIBE ROOM (GROUP CELEBRATION)
Purpose
Shared joy among birthday mates only
Duration
•	24 hours only

Allowed Interactions
•	Text messages
•	Emoji reactions
Excluded
•	Media uploads
•	Voice or video
•	Threads
•	Persistent chat history
The room prioritizes presence over performance.

9. PERSONAL BIRTHDAY ROOM (CORE EXPERIENCE)
Creation
•	Automatically available to celebrant on birthday day
•	Exists for 24 hours
Participants
Birthday Mates
•	Auto present
•	Clearly labeled
Invited Guests
•	Join via celebrant generated invite link
•	Must register or log in
•	Clearly labeled as “Guest”
Invite Rules
•	Only celebrant can generate links
•	Room specific
•	Time limited
•	Guest count limits
•	Guests cannot invite others

10. BIRTHDAY WALL (PHOTO CELEBRATION SPACE)
Purpose
A beautiful, temporary photo memory wall
Rules
•	Created manually by celebrant
•	Photos only (no video)
•	Limited uploads
•	Opens 24 hours before birthday
•	Closes 48 hours after birthday
Access
•	View only
•	Shareable public link
•	Emoji reactions allowed
•	No comments in V1
Beautification
•	Themes
•	Frames
•	Accent colors
•	Subtle animations

11. 1 ON 1 BIRTHDAY BUDDY
Purpose
Guarantee at least one meaningful connection
Rules
•	One automatic pairing per birthday
•	Birthday mates only
•	Text only
•	Anonymous until first message
•	No rematching
•	Can be ignored

12. STATE LEVEL CELEBRANT VISIBILITY
Default Mode
•	“X people are celebrating today in your state”
•	No names or profiles
Opt In Mode
•	Users may enable visibility
•	Shows name + profile picture
•	Visibility lasts 24 hours
Exclusions
•	No maps
•	No distances
•	No direct contact

13. PRE BIRTHDAY AWARENESS
Allowed
