15. MONETIZATION SYSTEM
A. Platform Owned Digital Gifts (PRIMARY)
•	Premium digital cards
•	Confetti & animation effects
•	Birthday wall highlights
•	Temporary celebrant badges
•	Featured message placement
B. Third Party Digital Gifts (SECONDARY)
•	Gift cards (Amazon, Netflix, Spotify, etc.)
•	API / affiliate based
•	Instant delivery
•	No inventory
C. Platform-Branded Merchandise (Non-Marketplace)
• T-shirts, hoodies, mugs
• Happy Birthday Mate–owned designs only
• Examples:
– “Kings Are Born in June”
– “Queens Are Born in June”
• Produced and fulfilled by third-party print-on-demand partners (Printful / Gelato)
• No third-party sellers, storefronts, or listings
16. PAYMENT INFRASTRUCTURE
•	Stripe (global)
